name: Skillshot (Canceled)
blurb: Skillshot is an addictive skill based game that will frustrate you, make you extra competitive and make you want to perfect each level.

rewards.reward: CAFFEINE - Help us work by buying us more coffee! We love you for that xx

SKILL - You just got 3 stars by perfecting the art of giving. Thank you. You get a digital thank you on youtube for helping us in our development AND an early copy of the game on your chosen platform!

TENNER - wow, thank you for your kindness. Here is a virtual hug from us all >0<. FAMILY - Congratulations you are now my brother or sister. Pledging this much makes you family to me and I thank you greatly! TOO KIND - Wow, really, you are just too kind. We want you to feel special so we will add your name into the special "too kind backers" levels.
